@ilopezfr You don't need an enterprise account to make this change yourself using your own github account. 

Follow https://github.com/apache/incubator-airflow/pull/2331 as an example. Also, please try to follow https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/AIRFLOW/Contributors%27+Guide

Be sure to squash your commits as well.

![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1684343/26606226/f938779c-4545-11e7-84db-84e35843a1f5.png)


It is pretty hard to tell lime from green in larger DAGs.

@saguziel Any idea how I can get into Airflow JIRA to make an issue?
